title: Plays of the Week: Week 7
text:
Plays of the Week: Week 7 - WVVA TV Bluefield Beckley WV News, Weather and Sports Member Center: Plays of the Week: Week 7 Posted: What are the plays of the week from Week 7? Fayetteville Dalton Dempsey TD Run Graham Jamorya Cousin fumble return TD Richlands Cody Howie catch and hurdle 
Thank you for participating in our poll! AP College Football Rankings In this week's Associated Press Poll, Baylor moves ahead of fellow Big 12 competitor TCU for the No. 2 ranking in the country. WVU will see both these teams back-to-back starting at Baylor on Saturday. And as it's been all season, Ohio State remains the top-ranked team.
